description:
Tsukiyama Minako is both Editor-in-Chief and president for the Lillian Kawaraban, the school`s newspaper. She is hyperactive, dedicated to her duty as president, always thinking of new ways to get the newest scoop, and can at times give http://anidb.net/ch1192 [Yumi] an uneasy feeling.
Source: Wikipedia
name: Tsukiyama Minako
